data.description: This Custom Home features the best of both worlds! One that it has an open floor plan, and two it has private areas that include an office for those that work from home, and a handsome library for the reader in the house! A split bedroom floor plan includes 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an Office, and a Library makes for plenty of space to enjoy! The Kitchen has a gas cooktop, built-in oven and microwave, center island, and a large, gorgeous skylight over the kitchen island that illuminates the main living areas!! The Office has a custom built-in desk and cabinetry all behind double French doors. The library has a custom built-in window seat with storage and custom built-in bookcases. The spacious Master Bath features two separate sink vanities, garden/soaking tub, separate shower, and a large walk-in closet. The fenced backyard has a covered patio that features a natural gas connection for your grill, so you will no longer need to fill those propane tanks! Come see this home today!
